<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>搜尋結果 - Taipei Fun Finder</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      color: #6c757d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Taipei Fun Finder 台北最新活動</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="mb-3">搜尋結果</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">為您找到 <%= results.length %> 筆符合條件的活動。</p>
    <hr class="mb-4">

    <% if (results.length > 0) { %>
      <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 row-cols-xl-4 g-4">
        <% results.forEach(event => { %>
          <%- include('partials/eventCard', { event: event }) %>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    <% } else { %>
      <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
        很抱歉，找不到符合您搜尋條件的活動。請試試其他關鍵字！
      </div>
    <% } %>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary mt-4">返回首頁</a>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer mt-5 py-4 bg-secondary text-white">
    </footer>
</body>
</html>